  "Description": {
    "English": "High-impact projectile weapon. Launched plasma shells bounce off surfaces until their internal timer triggers a large explosion.<br> <br>Charged with <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Unstable Plasma</span>. Careless use can result in damage to user.<br> <br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> to activate.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "高强度抛射武器。所发射的等离子弹从表面弹开，直到其内部定时器激活大爆炸。<br> <br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定的等离子</span>可给本设备充能。请小心使用，不然可能会对使用者造成伤害。<br> <br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 激活。",
    "TencentChinese": "高强度抛射武器。所发射的等离子弹从表面弹开，直到其内部定时器激活。<br> <br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定的等离子</span>可给本设备充能。请小心使用，不然可能会对使用者造成伤害。<br> <br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 激活。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "高衝擊射彈武器。發射持續將彈殼彈回的電漿彈，直到內部計時器啟動大爆炸。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不穩定電漿</span>補充。使用時如果不小心，可能會傷害使用者。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 啟動。"
  },
